\forall n \in \mathbb N
\sum_{m = 0}^{n} \left(\frac{n!}{m!(n-m)!}\right)^2=\frac{(2n)!}{(n!)^2}
\sum_{m=0}^n\binom{n}m^2=\binom{2n}n\;.
